# isEnabled

**Instance Property**

A Boolean value that enables and disables the bar button.

## Declaration

```swift
var isEnabled: Bool { get set }
```

## Discussion

The default value is [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/Swift/true].

## Configuring the Button

- **image**: The image displayed on the bar button.
- **title**: The title displayed on the bar button.
